        "collapsible_tab_MhnGWV": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Product Features",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p><strong>Bladeless fan with ambient light, shaking head </strong></p><p>1. Pioneering dual fan and dual duct design, providing stronger wind power. </p><p>2. Three phase brushless motor, quieter, rotates smoothly, and has no lag. </p><p>3. Leafless design, suitable for mother and baby, safe and worry free. </p><p>4. 9-speed wind speed, thoughtful gear memory function, caring about your usage habits.</p><p> 5. Press and hold to turn on, press and hold to turn off any gear. </p><p>6. Shake your head around 60 degrees to achieve wide-angle air supply, with a wider coverage, making coolness everywhere. </p><p>7. 9-hour timed schedule </p><p>8. 3-speed ambient night light adjustment, independent operation (turn off win</p><p>d speed, night light can also be turned on)9. Spray humidification design, cooling and water supplement more delicate. </p><p>Detachable water tank, more convenient to use (optional).</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
