            "block_heading": "Solid purchase",
            "text_1": "<p>This remote control airplane is exactly what we needed for our 10-year-old. As a first rc airplane, it's perfect - the foam construction makes it durable, and the simple controls make it easy to learn. It's a great drone for kids that focuses on pure flying fun without complicated cameras or GPS. Highly recommend this airplane for any beginner! ★★★★★</p>",
