        "text_JqUDnm": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>You're on back-to-back Zoom calls. Your ceiling fan just moves hot air around. The AC cools the whole room but kills your electricity bill. And a regular table fan? </p><p><strong>One nudge from your kid or pet and someone gets hurt.</strong> <br/><br/>That's the WFH summer trap most Indians are stuck in. AirLuxe was built to end it. <br/><br/>No blades. No noise. No guilt about your electricity bill. Just clean, steady cool airflow — exactly where you need it, exactly when you need it.</p>",
