        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n.user-benefits-wrapper {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f9fafb);\n  padding: 44px 20px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  max-width: 1100px;\n  margin: 50px auto;\n  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n}\n\n/* Section Header */\n.user-benefits-header {\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 38px;\n}\n\n.section-pill {\n  display: inline-block;\n  padding: 10px 22px;\n  background: #111827;\n  color: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  letter-spacing: 0.4px;\n  margin-bottom: 16px;\n}\n\n.user-benefits-header h2 {\n  font-size: 30px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #111827;\n}\n\n/* Grid */\n.user-benefits-grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));\n  gap: 26px;\n}\n\n/* Cards */\n.user-benefit-card {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 18px;\n  padding: 26px 24px;\n  box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);\n  transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.user-benefit-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-6px);\n}\n\n/* Pills */\n.user-pill {\n  display: inline-block;\n  padding: 6px 14px;\n  background: #ecfeff;\n  color: #155e75;\n  border-radius: 999px;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n/* Text */\n.user-benefit-text {\n  font-size: 15px;\n  line-height: 1.65;\n  color: #4b5563;\n}\n\n/* Meta */\n.user-meta {\n  margin-top: 14px;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  color: #6b7280;\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n\n/* Mobile */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .user-benefits-header h2 {\n    font-size: 24px;\n  }\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"user-benefits-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"user-benefits-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-pill\">REAL RESULTS</div>\n    <h2>How Users Have Benefitted</h2>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"user-benefits-grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"user-benefit-card\">\n      <div class=\"user-pill\">Office Comfort</div>\n      <div class=\"user-benefit-text\">\n        Users report noticeable relief from neck and shoulder stiffness caused by long hours of desk work and screen time.\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"user-meta\">— IT Professionals & WFH Users</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"user-benefit-card\">\n      <div class=\"user-pill\">Better Sleep</div>\n      <div class=\"user-benefit-text\">\n        Evening massage sessions help users unwind faster, release tension, and feel more relaxed before bedtime.\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"user-meta\">— Daily Stress Relief Users</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"user-benefit-card\">\n      <div class=\"user-pill\">Reduced Muscle Tightness</div>\n      <div class=\"user-benefit-text\">\n        Regular use helps ease tight shoulder and upper back muscles, especially after long travel or physical activity.\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"user-meta\">— Travelers & Active Individuals</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"user-benefit-card\">\n      <div class=\"user-pill\">Quick Relaxation</div>\n      <div class=\"user-benefit-text\">\n        Many users feel calmer and more refreshed within minutes, making it ideal for short breaks during busy days.\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"user-meta\">— Busy Professionals</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"user-benefit-card\">\n      <div class=\"user-pill\">Home Therapy</div>\n      <div class=\"user-benefit-text\">\n        Customers love having a convenient massage solution at home without the need for frequent spa visits.\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"user-meta\">— Home Wellness Users</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"user-benefit-card\">\n      <div class=\"user-pill\">Thoughtful Gifting</div>\n      <div class=\"user-benefit-text\">\n        Gift recipients often describe it as one of the most useful and relaxing wellness gifts they’ve received.\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"user-meta\">— Gift Buyers</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
    },
